column2: 36Kr Holdings, Inc. operates as an online media publisher offering new economy focused content. The company is headquartered in Beijing, Beijing and currently employs 478 full-time employees. The firm provides reports on companies, market updates, editorials and commentaries, and introduces some startup companies to the investment community. The firm offer services either through agencies or directly to the end customers. The firm operates its businesses primarily in the domestic market.
5-6/F Tower A1,Junhao Central, Park Plaza No.10 South Chaoyng, Park Avenue Chaoyang District
